    "en": {
      "title": "Many decided to withdraw from the referendum",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The main opposition United People's Shakti has decided to stay out of the referendum as the referendum on the interim relief proposed by President Ranil Wickremesinghe is scheduled to take place today.",
        "Meanwhile, Member of Parliament G. L. said that 13 members of parliament, including himself, who had decided to work independently in the opposition party, had decided to withdraw from the vote on interim relief. Peiris said. (R)"
      ],
